OL,3,CMan in hospital after fire at farm
OL,4,Caccommodation
OL,6,FA man is in hospital after a fire at
OL,7,Faccommodation on a Jersey farm.
OL,9,FThe fire started in a property on The
OL,10,FThree Oaks Vineries site on Sunday 19
OL,11,FJanuary.
OL,13,FNearby resident Clive Spurrier caught
OL,14,Fsight of the flames on Sunday morning
OL,15,Fand called 999.
OL,17,FHe explains: "I got myself dressed and
OL,18,Fran round to the accommodation, the
OL,19,Fentrance was the end that was on fire
OL,20,Freally badly so I couldn't get in.
