OL,3,CMan in hospital after fire at farm
OL,4,Caccommodation
OL,6,F"I was just shouting to see if I could
OL,7,Frouse anyone that was in there but
OL,8,Fthere was no answer."
OL,10,FA statement from Jersey Fire & Rescue
OL,11,Fsays: "Firefighters were called to a
OL,12,Fproperty in Grouville at approximately
OL,13,F7:15am on Sunday 19 January, after a
OL,14,Fneighbour reported seeing flames.
OL,16,F"When crews arrived, the property was
OL,17,Fwell alight. Firefighters entered in
OL,18,Fbreathing apparatus to locate the
OL,19,Fperson believed to be inside.
