OL,3,CMan in hospital after fire at farm
OL,4,Caccommodation
OL,6,F"One man was brought out to safety and
OL,7,Fthe fire was quickly brought under
OL,8,Fcontrol.
OL,10,F"The man was treated on-scene by the
OL,11,FStates of Jersey Fire and Rescue
OL,12,FService, before being handed over to
OL,13,FAmbulance crews and taken to hospital.
OL,15,F"The cause of the incident is under
OL,16,Finvestigation."
OL,18,FThe fire service says the man was
OL,19,Fliving at the accommodation and there
OL,20,Fwas a smoke alarm fitted but it was
OL,21,Fnot going off when crews arrived.
