OL,6,FIt is something firefighters say is
OL,7,Fbecoming more common when they attend
OL,8,Fincidents.
OL,10,FPhil Falle from the Service adds: "We
OL,11,Fwish to remind members of the public
OL,12,Fthat essentially every home, be it a
OL,13,Fone-bedroom flat or a very large
OL,14,Fproperty, needs to have smoke alarms
OL,15,Fwhich are working.
OL,17,F"They should be tested every month by
OL,18,Fpressing the button and they should be
OL,19,Fappropriately positioned. Every
OL,20,Fproperty should have at least one on
OL,21,Fevery level."
